{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-dang-006__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-dang-006", "source_id": "daya-dang-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·蕩之什·006.1", "text_original": "天生烝民，有物有則。民之秉彝，好是懿德。\n天監有周，昭假于下。保茲天子，生仲山甫。", "text_normalized": "天生烝民，有物有則。民之秉彝，好是懿德。\n天監有周，昭假于下。保茲天子，生仲山甫。", "notes": "烝民 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-dang-006__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-dang-006", "source_id": "daya-dang-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·蕩之什·006.2", "text_original": "仲山甫出祖，四牡業業，征夫捷捷。\n每懷靡及，四牡彭彭，八鸞鏘鏘。王命仲山甫，城彼東方。", "text_normalized": "仲山甫出祖，四牡業業，征夫捷捷。\n每懷靡及，四牡彭彭，八鸞鏘鏘。王命仲山甫，城彼東方。", "notes": "烝民 Chinese stanza 2."}
